headline: Howmet Aerospace Taps Geopolitics And AI Power Needs For Growth
summary: Howmet Aerospace (NYSE:HWM) is being highlighted as a mission critical supplier at the core of commercial and defense aviation and broader industrial infrastructure. The company is seeing rising demand tied to increased geopolitical spending and higher aftermarket activity across aerospace supply chains. Howmet’s industrial gas turbine business is experiencing accelerated orders linked to AI driven data center growth. The company continues to return cash to shareholders through an ongoing...

headline: Lockheed Martin (LMT) Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates (Revised)
summary: Lockheed (LMT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +19.07% and +2.48%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
